Dialogue: 7,0:16:02.26,0:16:05.35,Dial-JPN-TOP,,0,0,0,,28{\fscx50} {\fscx100}年目は{\fscx50} {\fscx100}31{\fscx50} {\fscx100}万{\fscx50} {\fscx100}7811{\fscx50} {\fscx100}匹
Dialogue: 8,0:16:05.35,0:16:08.29,Dial-CHI-TOP,,0,0,0,,第{\fscx50} {\fscx100}29{\fscx50} {\fscx100}年是{\fscx50} {\fscx100}51{\fscx50} {\fscx100}万{\fscx50} {\fscx100}4229{\fscx50} {\fscx100}头
Dialogue: 7,0:16:05.35,0:16:08.29,Dial-JPN-TOP,,0,0,0,,29{\fscx50} {\fscx100}年目は{\fscx50} {\fscx100}51{\fscx50} {\fscx100}万{\fscx50} {\fscx100}4229{\fscx50} {\fscx100}匹
